  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hordes are rising, only you stand in their way. Shoot, grind, slide, and jump your way around a multi-layered level against endless legions of demons, fiends, and monsters.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rise, fall, and rise again. Can you survive the <i><strong>Devil's Derby</strong></i>?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/f20ef419a6c4c03ef96cfb53efb6b1e4.avif?t=1756719748\" alt=\"Shoot\" width=1560 height=117 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/ae946de6940e37516efb2b3df0d7bc3f.poster.avif?t=1756719748\" width=780 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/ae946de6940e37516efb2b3df0d7bc3f.webm?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/ae946de6940e37516efb2b3df0d7bc3f.mp4?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your weapons to tear through endless demons and fiends. Lay down constant damage with the SMG, whilst blasting enemies away with the handcannon- charge it up to cause even more damage with an energy explosion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/eb13fa6459a5fb2d9dcf5e29c2e87c1a.avif?t=1756719748\" alt=\"Skate\" width=1560 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/d4aef8466053d50214c32ae95c0d382a.poster.avif?t=1756719748\" width=780 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/d4aef8466053d50214c32ae95c0d382a.webm?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/d4aef8466053d50214c32ae95c0d382a.mp4?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your momentum going by grinding around the many rails in the arena. Use them to your advantage to quickly reach other platforms and escape enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/8f147ce68634a6f50b63d95721529e1d.avif?t=1756719748\" alt=\"Slide\" width=1560 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/19d53dd26bcbc0de0db490189c24aea3.poster.avif?t=1756719748\" width=780 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/19d53dd26bcbc0de0db490189c24aea3.webm?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/19d53dd26bcbc0de0db490189c24aea3.mp4?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the master of the arena by using advance movement techniques to maintain your speed and stay aerial. Double jumps, wall runs, slides, blast jumps, bounces, and dashes- you will need to use all of these to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/05aad5b475b595dd8cd39c44efa2e5f5.avif?t=1756719748\" alt=\"Survive\" width=1560 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/1a741d6b254a834b69f987818d6debf5.poster.avif?t=1756719748\" width=780 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/1a741d6b254a834b69f987818d6debf5.webm?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/1a741d6b254a834b69f987818d6debf5.mp4?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight hordes of fiends intent on ending your life. From charging beasts who will tear you apart, to flying fiends ready to spit acid on you, to giant worms flying above the arena raining death and destruction. You will need to kill them all.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced first person shooter combat on skates.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One life, one level, one score.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, blast, and bash enemies with your SMG and hand cannon.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Higher scores upgrade your SMG during the run.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance movement techniques- slides, dashes, grinds, bounces, blast jumps, and wall runs.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for high score with your friends or globally on the leaderboard.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against a variety of demonic enemies- from small floating heads to gigantic flying worms.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hordes are rising, only you stand in their way. Shoot, grind, slide, and jump your way around a multi-layered level against endless legions of demons, fiends, and monsters.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rise, fall, and rise again. Can you survive the <i><strong>Devil's Derby</strong></i>?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/f20ef419a6c4c03ef96cfb53efb6b1e4.avif?t=1756719748\" alt=\"Shoot\" width=1560 height=117 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/ae946de6940e37516efb2b3df0d7bc3f.poster.avif?t=1756719748\" width=780 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/ae946de6940e37516efb2b3df0d7bc3f.webm?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/ae946de6940e37516efb2b3df0d7bc3f.mp4?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your weapons to tear through endless demons and fiends. Lay down constant damage with the SMG, whilst blasting enemies away with the handcannon- charge it up to cause even more damage with an energy explosion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/eb13fa6459a5fb2d9dcf5e29c2e87c1a.avif?t=1756719748\" alt=\"Skate\" width=1560 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/d4aef8466053d50214c32ae95c0d382a.poster.avif?t=1756719748\" width=780 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/d4aef8466053d50214c32ae95c0d382a.webm?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/d4aef8466053d50214c32ae95c0d382a.mp4?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your momentum going by grinding around the many rails in the arena. Use them to your advantage to quickly reach other platforms and escape enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/8f147ce68634a6f50b63d95721529e1d.avif?t=1756719748\" alt=\"Slide\" width=1560 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/19d53dd26bcbc0de0db490189c24aea3.poster.avif?t=1756719748\" width=780 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/19d53dd26bcbc0de0db490189c24aea3.webm?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/19d53dd26bcbc0de0db490189c24aea3.mp4?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the master of the arena by using advance movement techniques to maintain your speed and stay aerial. Double jumps, wall runs, slides, blast jumps, bounces, and dashes- you will need to use all of these to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/05aad5b475b595dd8cd39c44efa2e5f5.avif?t=1756719748\" alt=\"Survive\" width=1560 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/1a741d6b254a834b69f987818d6debf5.poster.avif?t=1756719748\" width=780 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/1a741d6b254a834b69f987818d6debf5.webm?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121580/extras/1a741d6b254a834b69f987818d6debf5.mp4?t=1756719748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight hordes of fiends intent on ending your life. From charging beasts who will tear you apart, to flying fiends ready to spit acid on you, to giant worms flying above the arena raining death and destruction. You will need to kill them all.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced first person shooter combat on skates.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One life, one level, one score.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, blast, and bash enemies with your SMG and hand cannon.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Higher scores upgrade your SMG during the run.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance movement techniques- slides, dashes, grinds, bounces, blast jumps, and wall runs.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for high score with your friends or globally on the leaderboard.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against a variety of demonic enemies- from small floating heads to gigantic flying worms.</p></li></ul>",
